"{\"uid\": \"oann.com-newsroom-paris-olympics-michael-phelps-disappointed-in-mens-usa-swimming-performance\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"OAN StaffBlake Wolf3:21 PM - Wednesday, August 7, 2024  Aside from a few standout swimmers, Michael Phelps expressed his disappointment in the Men's USA swimming results at the Paris Olympic games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 3, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OAN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0489403528274365e-27, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me as a whole, I was pretty disappointed to see the U.S. swimming results,\\\" Phelps said in an Interview withUSA Today.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, there were a few standout swims, and those you have to recognize.\\\"\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Phelps did praise swimmer Bobby Finke for his \\\"unbelievable\\\" performance in the 1500-meter freestyle swim, which resulted in a gold medal as well as a new world record.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have chills right now talking about it,\\\" Phelps said, regarding Finke.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was one of the greatest swims in the Olympics, in my opinion.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able to break that world record in the [manner] that he did it.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just taking it out, challenging the other guys just to make a move, he was prepared.\\\"\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the interview, Phelps also explained his concern for the future of the USA swimming team.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the things that I have always said over the last couple of years is the rest of the world is catching up,\\\" Phelps said.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a lot of the things that we have done as a country for so long, the other people are catching up.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are doing the same thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23x gold medal swimmer then issued an open challenge for American swimmers looking to obtain the same level of greatness as Phelps has achieved.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999340998620937, \"rank\": 4.966580370070895e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone thought what I was trying to do was impossible, and if somebody's trying to do it now, you guys will all say it's impossible,\\\" Phelps continued.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If somebody wants to do it and they want it bad enough, and they are willing to take the little baby steps that it takes to get there, then I want to see it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps concluded the interview by saying, \\\"Records are made to be broken.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The records that I was chasing throughout my career motivated me.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So hopefully I can motivate somebody to do the same thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay informed!\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Receive breaking news blasts directly to your inbox for free.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe here.https://www.oann.com/alerts    What do YOU think?\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click here to jump to the comments!\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this post!\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Accessibility Tools\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": []}]}"